             was indicted for <rs id="t18181028-175-off993" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18181028-175-off993" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18181028-175-off993" type="offenceSubcategory" value="theftFromPlace"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18181028-175-cd994" type="crimeDate">13th of October</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18181028-175-off993 t18181028-175-cd994"></join>, one silver cream jug, value 3l., and one table-spoon, value 10s., the goods of 
                     <persName id="t18181028-175-victim1175" type="victimName">
                        Claudius 
                        Chervat
                     <interp inst="t18181028-175-victim1175" type="surname" value="Chervat"></interp>
                        <interp inst="t18181028-175-victim1175" type="given" value="Claudius"></interp>
